snippet.title: LADB Restoration
snippet.description:
Welcome to LADB !
We create restoration videos ! Our mission is to entertain and to give you the opportunity to discover forgotten tools, with a focus on agricultural tools but not only ! Hopefully both at the same time !

Enjoy !
